(652, 'AA652', 'Internal: Provide (or attach) an organogram for the laboratory depicting the management structure and the interrelationship of all laboratory staff. External: Provide (or attach) an organizational diagram depicting the relationship of the laboratory within the broader laboratory network.', 'Internal: Provide (or attach) an organogram for the laboratory depicting the management structure and the interrelationship of all laboratory staff. External: Provide (or attach) an organizational diagram depicting the relationship of the laboratory within the broader laboratory network.', '', 'Ni b: Cung cp (hoc nh km) cu trc t chc cho phng th nghim m t c cu qun l v mi tng quan ca tt c cc nhn vin phng th nghim. Bn ngoi: Cung cp (hoc nh km) mt s  t chc m t mi quan h ca phng th nghim trong mng li phng th nghim rng ln hn.', 'Interne: Tracer (ou joindre) un organigramme du laboratoire prsentant la structure de la direction et les liens hirarchiques existant entre chacun des membres du personnel. Externe: Tracer (ou joindre) un organigramme dcrivant les relations du laboratoire avec les autres laboratoires du rseau'),
