(665, 'AA665', ' Confirm that each result or batch can be traced back to a corresponding internal quality control (IQC) run and that the IQC was passed. Confirm that IQC results are recorded for all IQC runs and reviewed for validation.', ' Confirm that each result or batch can be traced back to a corresponding internal quality control (IQC) run and that the IQC was passed. Confirm that IQC results are recorded for all IQC runs and reviewed for validation.', '', '', ''),
